## testing

```bash
ruff check --fix
ruff format
mypy .
pytest
```

## model sizes

| Model | Parameters | Layers | Heads | Embedding Dim |
|-------|------------|--------|-------|---------------|
| 124M  | 124M       | 12     | 12    | 768           |
| 355M  | 355M       | 24     | 16    | 1024          |
| 774M  | 774M       | 36     | 20    | 1280          |
| 1558M | 1558M      | 48     | 25    | 1600          |

